## 📁 PROJECT STRUCTURE CONVENTIONS

```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── ui/                   # Primitives (Button, Card, Input, …)
│   │   ├── layout/               # Navigation, Footer, PageWrapper
│   │   ├── sections/             # Page sections (Hero, Pricing, ROICalculator, ContactForm…)
│   │   ├── features/             # Feature blocks (PricingCard, ProfitCalculator…)
│   │   ├── seo/                  # SEO components (StructuredData, PageMeta, CanonicalLink)
│   │   └── figma/                # Figma-related (ImageWithFallback)
│   ├── pages/                    # Route-level pages
│   ├── shared/
│   │   └── constants/            # navigation.ts, seo.ts, packages.ts
│   ├── App.tsx
│   └── routes.tsx
│
├── hooks/                        # Custom hooks (useContactForm, useRoiCalc…)
├── services/                     # External integrations (telegram.ts, leads.ts)
├── lib/                          # SDK instances (pocketbase.ts)
├── types/                        # Shared TypeScript types/interfaces
├── styles/                       # globals: index.css, tailwind.css, theme.css, fonts.css
├── assets/
│   ├── images/                   # WebP/AVIF images
│   └── fonts/                    # Self-hosted font files
└── main.tsx
```

